<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="ja">
<head>
<meta charset="utf-8">
<meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1, maximum-scale=1">
<title>7月の勉強時間パーソナル診断｜受験の王様 × THINKING</title>
<meta name="description" content="6問タップするだけで、あなた専用の7月の最低勉強時間（MIN）とタイプ別の戦い方がわかる無料診断。回答するたびに数字が絞り込まれます。">
<meta property="og:title" content="7月の勉強時間パーソナル診断">
<meta property="og:description" content="学年×部活×志望校で答えは全員違う。6問・約1分で、あなた専用のMINが出ます。">
<link rel="preconnect" href="https://fonts.googleapis.com">
<link rel="preconnect" href="https://fonts.gstatic.com" crossorigin>
<link href="https://fonts.googleapis.com/css2?family=Noto+Sans+JP:wght@400;500;700;900&family=Noto+Serif+JP:wght@600;900&display=swap" rel="stylesheet">
<style>
:root{
  --navy:#1B2A4A;
  --navy-deep:#12203B;
  --gold:#C9A227;
  --gold-light:#F3E7C3;
  --vermilion:#D6452B;
  --green:#2E7D4F;
  --paper:#FBF8F1;
  --ink:#26282E;
  --line:#DDD6C6;
  --serif:"Noto Serif JP",serif;
  --sans:"Noto Sans JP",sans-serif;
}
*{margin:0;padding:0;box-sizing:border-box;-webkit-tap-highlight-color:transparent;}
html{font-size:16px;}
body{
  font-family:var(--sans);
  color:var(--ink);
  background:
    linear-gradient(rgba(27,42,74,.05) 1px, transparent 1px),
    linear-gradient(90deg, rgba(27,42,74,.05) 1px, transparent 1px),
    var(--paper);
  background-size:22px 22px,22px 22px,auto;
  min-height:100dvh;
  line-height:1.75;
}
.app{
  max-width:480px;
  margin:0 auto;
  min-height:100dvh;
  display:flex;
  flex-direction:column;
  position:relative;
}

/* ===== ヘッダー ===== */
header{
  padding:14px 20px 8px;
  display:flex;
  align-items:center;
  justify-content:space-between;
}
.brand{
  font-family:var(--serif);
  font-weight:900;
  color:var(--navy);
  font-size:.95rem;
  letter-spacing:.22em;
}
.brand small{
  display:block;
  font-family:var(--sans);
  font-weight:500;
  font-size:.6rem;
  letter-spacing:.14em;
  color:#8b8574;
}
.hozon{
  background:var(--vermilion);
  color:#fff;
  font-weight:700;
  font-size:.65rem;
  letter-spacing:.12em;
  padding:4px 10px 3px;
  clip-path:polygon(0 0,100% 0,100% 100%,50% 82%,0 100%);
}

/* ===== 進捗 ===== */
.progress-wrap{padding:0 20px;height:26px;}
.progress-row{
  display:flex;justify-content:space-between;align-items:center;
  font-size:.7rem;color:#8b8574;font-weight:500;letter-spacing:.08em;
}
.progress-row .back-btn{
  background:none;border:none;color:var(--navy);
  font-family:var(--sans);font-size:.75rem;font-weight:700;
  cursor:pointer;padding:2px 4px;visibility:hidden;
}
.progress-row .back-btn.show{visibility:visible;}
.pbar{
  height:4px;background:#E7E1D1;border-radius:2px;overflow:hidden;margin-top:2px;
}
.pbar i{
  display:block;height:100%;width:0%;
  background:linear-gradient(90deg,var(--navy),var(--gold));
  transition:width .45s cubic-bezier(.22,1,.36,1);
}

/* ===== 画面共通 ===== */
main{flex:1;position:relative;overflow:hidden;padding-bottom:130px;}
.screen{
  position:absolute;inset:0;
  padding:6px 20px 24px;
  opacity:0;transform:translateX(28px);
  pointer-events:none;
  transition:opacity .32s ease,transform .32s cubic-bezier(.22,1,.36,1);
  overflow-y:auto;
}
.screen.active{opacity:1;transform:translateX(0);pointer-events:auto;}

/* ===== スタート画面 ===== */
.start-frame{
  border:1.5px solid var(--gold);
  background:var(--navy-deep);
  color:#fff;
  padding:30px 22px 24px;
  text-align:center;
  margin-top:6px;
  position:relative;
}
.start-kicker{
  color:var(--gold);
  font-size:.75rem;
  letter-spacing:.38em;
  margin-bottom:12px;
  font-weight:500;
}
.start-title{
  font-family:var(--serif);
  font-weight:900;
  font-size:1.9rem;
  line-height:1.4;
  letter-spacing:.03em;
}
.start-title em{font-style:normal;color:#FF6B4A;}
.start-sub{
  margin-top:12px;
  font-size:.84rem;
  color:#D8D2C2;
  line-height:2;
}
.start-sub b{color:var(--gold);}
.start-points{
  display:flex;gap:8px;margin-top:20px;
}
.start-points div{
  flex:1;border:1px solid rgba(255,255,255,.3);
  padding:10px 4px;font-size:.68rem;line-height:1.5;color:#E8E2D2;
}
.start-points b{
  display:block;color:var(--gold);
  font-family:var(--serif);font-size:.95rem;margin-bottom:2px;
}
.countdown{
  margin-top:16px;
  font-size:.75rem;color:#C8C2B2;letter-spacing:.1em;
}
.countdown b{
  font-family:var(--serif);color:#FF6B4A;font-size:1.15rem;padding:0 2px;
}
.start-note{
  text-align:center;font-size:.72rem;color:#8b8574;margin-top:12px;
}
.btn-primary{
  display:block;width:100%;
  margin-top:18px;
  background:var(--vermilion);
  color:#fff;border:none;cursor:pointer;
  font-family:var(--sans);font-weight:900;font-size:1.05rem;
  letter-spacing:.14em;
  padding:16px;
  border-radius:4px;
  box-shadow:0 4px 0 #A33017;
  transition:transform .08s,box-shadow .08s;
}
.btn-primary:active{transform:translateY(3px);box-shadow:0 1px 0 #A33017;}

/* ===== 質問画面 ===== */
.q-eyebrow{
  display:inline-block;
  background:var(--navy);color:#fff;
  font-family:var(--serif);font-weight:600;
  font-size:.72rem;letter-spacing:.18em;
  padding:3px 12px;margin-bottom:10px;
}
.q-text{
  font-family:var(--serif);
  font-weight:900;
  font-size:1.26rem;
  color:var(--navy);
  line-height:1.55;
  margin-bottom:6px;
}
.q-hint{font-size:.76rem;color:#8b8574;margin-bottom:14px;}
.opts{display:flex;flex-direction:column;gap:10px;}
.opt{
  display:flex;align-items:center;justify-content:space-between;gap:10px;
  width:100%;text-align:left;
  background:#fff;
  border:1.5px solid var(--line);
  border-left:4px solid var(--navy);
  border-radius:4px;
  padding:13px 14px;
  font-family:var(--sans);
  font-size:.92rem;font-weight:700;color:var(--ink);
  cursor:pointer;
  transition:transform .1s,border-color .15s,background .15s;
}
.opt small{
  display:block;font-weight:500;font-size:.72rem;color:#8b8574;line-height:1.5;
}
.opt .mark{
  flex:none;width:22px;height:22px;border-radius:50%;
  border:2px solid var(--line);
  display:flex;align-items:center;justify-content:center;
  font-size:.7rem;color:transparent;
  transition:all .15s;
}
.opt:active{transform:scale(.985);}
.opt.selected{
  border-color:var(--vermilion);
  border-left-color:var(--vermilion);
  background:#FDF3EF;
}
.opt.selected .mark{
  border-color:var(--vermilion);
  background:var(--vermilion);
  color:#fff;
}

/* ===== ティザーチップ ===== */
.teaser{
  position:fixed;
  bottom:118px;left:50%;
  transform:translate(-50%,14px);
  width:calc(100% - 40px);max-width:440px;
  background:var(--navy);
  border-left:4px solid var(--gold);
  color:#fff;
  font-size:.8rem;font-weight:700;
  line-height:1.6;
  padding:10px 14px;
  border-radius:4px;
  box-shadow:0 6px 18px rgba(18,32,59,.35);
  opacity:0;
  pointer-events:none;
  transition:opacity .25s ease,transform .25s cubic-bezier(.22,1,.36,1);
  z-index:60;
}
.teaser.show{opacity:1;transform:translate(-50%,0);}
.teaser .tz-icon{color:var(--gold);margin-right:6px;}

/* ===== MINレンジメーター（固定フッター） ===== */
.meter{
  position:fixed;bottom:0;left:50%;transform:translateX(-50%);
  width:100%;max-width:480px;
  background:var(--navy-deep);
  color:#fff;
  padding:10px 20px 12px;
  border-top:2px solid var(--gold);
  z-index:50;
  transition:transform .4s cubic-bezier(.22,1,.36,1);
}
.meter.hidden{transform:translate(-50%,110%);}
.meter-label{
  font-size:.62rem;letter-spacing:.2em;color:var(--gold);
  text-align:center;font-weight:700;margin-bottom:6px;
}
.range-row{
  display:flex;align-items:center;gap:10px;
  margin-bottom:6px;
}
.range-row .cap{
  flex:none;width:2.4em;
  font-size:.7rem;color:#C8C2B2;font-weight:700;
}
.range-track{
  flex:1;height:12px;position:relative;
  background:rgba(255,255,255,.12);
  border-radius:6px;
}
.range-band{
  position:absolute;top:0;height:100%;
  background:linear-gradient(90deg,var(--gold),#E3C55A);
  border-radius:6px;
  transition:left .55s cubic-bezier(.22,1,.36,1),width .55s cubic-bezier(.22,1,.36,1),background .3s;
  min-width:10px;
}
.range-band.locked{background:var(--vermilion);}
.range-val{
  flex:none;width:5.4em;text-align:right;
  font-family:var(--serif);font-weight:900;font-size:.98rem;
  color:#fff;white-space:nowrap;
}
.range-val small{font-size:.64rem;font-weight:500;color:#C8C2B2;}
.range-val.locked{color:#FF8A6E;}
.meter-note{
  text-align:center;font-size:.6rem;color:#7d7a6e;letter-spacing:.06em;
}
.meter-note b{color:var(--gold);}

/* ===== 計測中アニメ ===== */
.calc-wrap{text-align:center;padding-top:64px;}
.calc-ring{
  width:84px;height:84px;margin:0 auto 20px;
  border:3px solid #E7E1D1;
  border-top-color:var(--vermilion);
  border-radius:50%;
  animation:spin 1s linear infinite;
}
@keyframes spin{to{transform:rotate(360deg);}}
.calc-text{
  font-family:var(--serif);font-weight:900;color:var(--navy);
  font-size:1.1rem;letter-spacing:.1em;
}
.calc-sub{font-size:.78rem;color:#8b8574;margin-top:6px;}

/* ===== 結果画面 ===== */
.result-head{text-align:center;margin:2px 0 12px;}
.result-head .rk{
  display:inline-block;
  background:var(--navy);color:#fff;
  font-family:var(--serif);font-size:.75rem;letter-spacing:.28em;
  padding:4px 16px;
}
/* スクショフレーム */
.shot-zone{
  position:relative;
  padding:14px 10px 12px;
}
.shot-zone::before,.shot-zone::after,
.shot-zone .corner-b::before,.shot-zone .corner-b::after{
  content:"";position:absolute;width:22px;height:22px;
  border-color:var(--vermilion);border-style:solid;
}
.shot-zone::before{top:0;left:0;border-width:3px 0 0 3px;}
.shot-zone::after{top:0;right:0;border-width:3px 3px 0 0;}
.shot-zone .corner-b::before{bottom:0;left:0;border-width:0 0 3px 3px;}
.shot-zone .corner-b::after{bottom:0;right:0;border-width:0 3px 3px 0;}
.shot-tag{
  position:absolute;top:-11px;left:50%;transform:translateX(-50%);
  background:var(--vermilion);color:#fff;
  font-size:.66rem;font-weight:900;letter-spacing:.14em;
  padding:3px 14px;border-radius:20px;
  white-space:nowrap;z-index:2;
}
.result-card{
  background:#fff;
  border:2.5px solid var(--navy);
  border-radius:6px;
  padding:20px 16px 14px;
  position:relative;
  text-align:center;
  box-shadow:0 3px 0 rgba(27,42,74,.15);
}
.result-min-label{
  font-size:.72rem;font-weight:700;color:var(--vermilion);
  letter-spacing:.2em;margin-bottom:4px;
}
.result-nums{display:flex;justify-content:center;gap:8px;}
.rnum{
  flex:1;
  border:1.5px dashed var(--line);
  border-radius:4px;
  padding:10px 4px 8px;
}
.rnum .cap{font-size:.72rem;color:#8b8574;font-weight:700;}
.rnum .big{
  font-family:var(--serif);font-weight:900;
  font-size:2.6rem;line-height:1.15;
  color:var(--navy);
}
.rnum.holiday .big{color:var(--vermilion);}
.rnum .unit{font-size:.8rem;font-weight:700;color:#8b8574;}
.type-line{
  margin-top:10px;
  font-size:.78rem;color:#555;
}
.type-line b{color:var(--vermilion);font-family:var(--serif);font-size:.9rem;}
.stamp{
  position:absolute;top:-14px;right:-4px;
  width:78px;height:78px;
  border:3px solid var(--vermilion);
  border-radius:50%;
  color:var(--vermilion);
  font-family:var(--serif);font-weight:900;
  display:flex;flex-direction:column;align-items:center;justify-content:center;
  background:rgba(251,248,241,.92);
  transform:rotate(9deg) scale(3);
  opacity:0;
  line-height:1.2;
  z-index:3;
}
.stamp .tname{font-size:1.15rem;letter-spacing:.05em;}
.stamp .tcap{font-size:.5rem;letter-spacing:.14em;}
.stamp.on{
  animation:stampIn .45s cubic-bezier(.34,1.4,.64,1) forwards;
  animation-delay:.85s;
}
@keyframes stampIn{
  0%{transform:rotate(9deg) scale(3);opacity:0;}
  60%{transform:rotate(-6deg) scale(.94);opacity:1;}
  100%{transform:rotate(-8deg) scale(1);opacity:1;}
}
.retire-note{
  margin-top:10px;
  background:var(--gold-light);
  border-left:3px solid var(--gold);
  font-size:.76rem;text-align:left;
  padding:8px 12px;border-radius:2px;
}
.retire-note b{color:var(--navy);}

/* 実現可能性バー */
.feas{
  margin-top:6px;
  background:#fff;border:1.5px solid var(--line);border-radius:6px;
  padding:13px 14px 11px;
}
.feas-title{
  font-size:.8rem;font-weight:900;color:var(--navy);margin-bottom:8px;
  letter-spacing:.04em;
}
.feas-bar{
  height:22px;background:#EFEAD9;border-radius:4px;overflow:hidden;display:flex;
}
.feas-bar .seg{
  height:100%;width:0%;
  transition:width .9s cubic-bezier(.22,1,.36,1);
  transition-delay:.3s;
}
.seg.desk{background:var(--navy);}
.seg.gap-seg{background:repeating-linear-gradient(45deg,var(--vermilion),var(--vermilion) 5px,#E8836E 5px,#E8836E 10px);}
.seg.slack{background:var(--green);}
.feas-legend{
  display:flex;gap:12px;flex-wrap:wrap;
  font-size:.66rem;color:#666;margin-top:7px;
}
.feas-legend i{
  display:inline-block;width:9px;height:9px;border-radius:2px;margin-right:4px;vertical-align:-1px;
}
.feas-msg{margin-top:8px;font-size:.78rem;line-height:1.7;}
.feas-msg.ok{color:var(--green);font-weight:700;}
.feas-msg.warn{color:var(--vermilion);font-weight:700;}
.feas-msg span{display:block;font-weight:500;color:#555;font-size:.74rem;}

/* ポイント */
.points{margin-top:8px;}
.points-title{
  font-family:var(--serif);font-weight:900;color:var(--navy);
  font-size:1.02rem;margin-bottom:10px;
  display:flex;align-items:center;gap:8px;
}
.points-title::after{content:"";flex:1;height:2px;background:var(--navy);}
.point{
  background:#fff;border:1.5px solid var(--line);border-radius:6px;
  padding:12px 14px;margin-bottom:9px;
  display:flex;gap:11px;align-items:flex-start;
}
.point .pn{
  flex:none;
  font-family:var(--serif);font-weight:900;
  color:#fff;background:var(--vermilion);
  width:26px;height:26px;border-radius:50%;
  display:flex;align-items:center;justify-content:center;
  font-size:.85rem;margin-top:2px;
}
.point .pt-body b{
  display:block;font-size:.88rem;color:var(--navy);line-height:1.5;margin-bottom:2px;
}
.point .pt-body p{font-size:.78rem;color:#555;line-height:1.7;}

/* CTA */
.cta{
  margin-top:20px;
  background:var(--navy-deep);
  border:1.5px solid var(--gold);
  border-radius:6px;
  color:#fff;
  padding:22px 16px 18px;
  text-align:center;
}
.cta-t{
  font-family:var(--serif);font-weight:900;color:var(--gold);
  font-size:1.12rem;letter-spacing:.05em;margin-bottom:10px;
  line-height:1.6;
}
.cta p{font-size:.82rem;color:#E8E2D2;line-height:1.95;}
.cta p b{color:#fff;}
.cta-step{display:flex;gap:6px;margin-top:14px;}
.cta-step div{
  flex:1;border:1px solid rgba(255,255,255,.28);
  font-size:.66rem;color:#D8D2C2;padding:9px 4px;line-height:1.55;
}
.cta-step b{display:block;color:var(--gold);font-size:.72rem;margin-bottom:2px;}
.btn-line{
  display:block;width:100%;margin-top:16px;
  background:#06C755;color:#fff;text-decoration:none;
  font-weight:900;font-size:.98rem;letter-spacing:.06em;
  padding:15px 8px;border-radius:4px;
  box-shadow:0 4px 0 #059B43;
  line-height:1.5;
}
.btn-line small{display:block;font-weight:700;font-size:.68rem;opacity:.9;}
.btn-line:active{transform:translateY(3px);box-shadow:0 1px 0 #059B43;}
.btn-retry{
  display:block;width:100%;margin-top:12px;
  background:none;border:1.5px solid var(--line);border-radius:4px;
  font-family:var(--sans);color:#8b8574;font-weight:700;font-size:.82rem;
  padding:11px;cursor:pointer;
}
.result-footer{
  text-align:center;font-size:.62rem;color:#a29a86;
  letter-spacing:.14em;margin:22px 0 10px;line-height:2;
}
.philosophy-line{
  font-family:var(--serif);font-weight:600;color:var(--navy);font-size:.8rem;letter-spacing:.12em;
}

@media (prefers-reduced-motion:reduce){
  *{animation-duration:.01ms!important;transition-duration:.01ms!important;}
}
</style>
</head>
<body>
<div class="app">

  <header>
    <div class="brand">受験の王様<small>オンライン塾 THINKING</small></div>
    <div class="hozon">保存版</div>
  </header>

  <div class="progress-wrap">
    <div class="progress-row">
      <button class="back-btn" id="backBtn" type="button">← 前の質問へ</button>
      <span id="progressText"></span>
    </div>
    <div class="pbar"><i id="pbarFill"></i></div>
  </div>

  <main id="main">

    <!-- スタート -->
    <section class="screen active" data-screen="start">
      <div class="start-frame">
        <div class="start-kicker">平均を信じた人から、落ちていく</div>
        <h1 class="start-title">あなたの7月、<br>1日<em>何時間</em>が正解？</h1>
        <p class="start-sub">学年 × 部活 × 志望校 × 今の偏差値。<br>組み合わせで答えは<b>全員違います。</b></p>
        <div class="start-points">
          <div><b>6問</b>タップだけ<br>約1分で完了</div>
          <div><b>回答ごと</b>に<br>数字が絞られる</div>
          <div><b>あなた専用</b>の<br>戦い方つき</div>
        </div>
        <div class="countdown" id="countdown"></div>
      </div>
      <button class="btn-primary" id="startBtn" type="button">自分の数字を出す →</button>
      <p class="start-note">画面下に「予測レンジ」が出ます。答えるほど狭まり、最後の1問で確定します。</p>
    </section>

    <!-- 質問（JSで生成） -->

    <!-- 計測中 -->
    <section class="screen" data-screen="calc">
      <div class="calc-wrap">
        <div class="calc-ring"></div>
        <div class="calc-text" id="calcText">あなたのMINを設計中…</div>
        <p class="calc-sub" id="calcSub">基礎ライン × 4つの補正を計算しています</p>
      </div>
    </section>

    <!-- 結果 -->
    <section class="screen" data-screen="result">
      <div class="result-head"><span class="rk">診 断 結 果</span></div>

      <div class="shot-zone">
        <span class="corner-b"></span>
        <span class="shot-tag">📸 ここをスクショ</span>

        <div class="result-card">
          <div class="stamp" id="stamp">
            <span class="tname" id="stampName"></span>
            <span class="tcap">7月タイプ</span>
          </div>
          <div class="result-min-label">7月のあなたの最低ライン（MIN）</div>
          <div class="result-nums">
            <div class="rnum">
              <div class="cap">平日</div>
              <div class="big" id="rWeekday">0</div>
              <div class="unit">時間／日</div>
            </div>
            <div class="rnum holiday">
              <div class="cap">休日</div>
              <div class="big" id="rHoliday">0</div>
              <div class="unit">時間／日</div>
            </div>
          </div>
          <div class="type-line" id="typeLine"></div>
          <div class="retire-note" id="retireNote" style="display:none;"></div>
